collector.data
Class Enregistrement

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--collector.data.Enregistrement
All Implemented Interfaces:
Element
public class Enregistrement
extends java.lang.Object
implements Element

An Enregistrement is an Array of Cell and an unique key. It is also an Element. An Enregistrement can inherit from one parent Enregistrement.
